OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy day with outbreaks of
OL,6,Frain or drizzle across Argyll.
OL,7,FElsewhere, a cloudy start with the odd
OL,8,Fspot of rain but becoming dry with
OL,9,Flengthening sunny spells and feeling
OL,10,Fwarm in the afternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA cloudy evening with patchy
OL,13,Frain across Argyll. Otherwise, a dry
OL,14,Fand bright end to the day, then dry
OL,15,Fwith lengthening clear spells
OL,16,Fovernight.
OL,17,
OL,18,CMonday:FA largely dry day with plenty
OL,19,Fof sunshine and feeling warm. Cloudier
OL,20,Fwith patchy rain across north Argyll
OL,21,Fand Lochaber.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
